reat , King of Macedon (  356–323  bc  ), around whom a large body of popular legend grew up in late antiquity, much of which came to be embodied in the medieval ‘Alexander romances’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Alexander Chisholm was born in 1190, in Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1248, in his hometown, at the age of 58."},"et":{"1190–1248":"1190–1248","1210–1254":"1210–1254","1190":"1190","1248":"1248","1254":"1254","1210":"1210","Chisholm, Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1190–1248":"1190–1248","1210–1254":"1210–1254","1190":"1190","1248":"1248","1254":"1254","1210":"1210","Chisholm, Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1190–1248":"1190–1248","1210–1254":"1210–1254","1190":"1190","1248":"1248","1254":"1254","1210":"1210","Chisholm, Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Alexander Chisholm est né en 1190, à Roxburghshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1248, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 58 ans."},"de":{"1190–1248":"1190–1248","1210–1254":"1210–1254","1190":"1190","1248":"1248","1254":"1254","1210":"1210","Chisholm, Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Schottland, United Kingdom","Roxburghshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Roxburghshire, Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Alexander Chisholm wurde 1190 in Roxburghshire, Schottland, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1248 im Alter von 58 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1190–1248":"1190–1248","1210–1254":"1210–1254","1190":"1190","1248":"1248","1254":"